bug.short_desc: [api] move classes in org.eclipse.mylyn.internal.provisional.tasks.core to API package

long_desc.thetext: TasksUtil.encode()/decode() should move to CoreUtil and RepositoryManager should either be fixed or removed.
TasksUtil.encode() and TasksUtil.decode() have been moved to CoreUtil and marked deprecated. The deprecated provisional methods will likely be remove in 3.9.
RepositoryClientManager is now located in org.eclipse.mylyn.tasks.core and extensible. See bug 378855 for details.
